{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/title"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"copy"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"readonly"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"title"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Although this property is optional, if you support the selection of annotations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"in your map view, you are expected to provide this property. This string is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed in the callout for the associated annotation.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"title","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"title","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"title","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNAnnotation(py)title"},"abstract":[{"text":"The string containing the annotation’s title.","type":"text"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/title"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation/title":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/title","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/title","fragments":[{"text":"title","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","